channel.title: Project Insanity Webclient
channel.description: I'm trying to make a project insanity webclient and I'm having troubles. Mainly, all tutorials autocachedownloaders are either removed from mediafire or deleted from the page they're on for some reason. If anybody can either just make my client auto download the cache or point me to a working link for a tutorial, it would be greatly appreciated. I will reimburse you in some way if you make my client auto download.
